7124 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7125 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(31)) << 21;
7126 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(32)) >> 5;
7127 // op: XB
7128 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
7129 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(31)) << 11;
7130 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(32)) >> 4;
7131 // op: UIM5
7132 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
7133 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7134 op <<= 16;
7135 Value |= op;
7136 break;
7137 }
7138 case PPC::XXINSERTW: {
7139 // op: XT
7140 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7141 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(31)) << 21;
7142 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(32)) >> 5;
7143 // op: XB
7144 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
7145 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(31)) << 11;
7146 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(32)) >> 4;
7147 // op: UIM5
7148 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(3), Fixups, STI);
7149 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7150 op <<= 16;
7151 Value |= op;
7152 break;
7153 }
7154 case PPC::PLXV:
7155 case PPC::PSTXV: {
7156 // op: XT
7157 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7158 op &= UINT64_C(63);
7159 op <<= 21;
7160 Value |= op;
7161 // op: D_RA
7162 op = getMemRI34Encoding(MI, 1, Fixups, STI);
7163 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(17179803648)) << 16;
7164 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(532575944704)) >> 18;
7165 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(65535));
7166 break;
7167 }
7168 case PPC::PLXVpc:
7169 case PPC::PSTXVpc: {
7170 // op: XT
7171 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7172 op &= UINT64_C(63);
7173 op <<= 21;
7174 Value |= op;
7175 // op: D_RA
7176 op = getMemRI34PCRelEncoding(MI, 1, Fixups, STI);
7177 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(17179803648)) << 16;
7178 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(532575944704)) >> 18;
7179 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(65535));
7180 break;
7181 }
7182 case PPC::MFVRD:
7183 case PPC::MFVRWZ:
7184 case PPC::MFVSRD:
7185 case PPC::MFVSRLD:
7186 case PPC::MFVSRWZ: {
7187 // op: XT
7188 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
7189 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(31)) << 21;
7190 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(32)) >> 5;
7191 // op: A
7192 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7193 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7194 op <<= 16;
7195 Value |= op;
7196 break;
7197 }
7198 case PPC::LXVPX:
7199 case PPC::STXVPX: {
7200 // op: XTp
7201 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7202 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 22;
7203 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 17;
7204 // op: A
7205 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
7206 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7207 op <<= 16;
7208 Value |= op;
7209 // op: B
7210 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
7211 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7212 op <<= 11;
7213 Value |= op;
7214 break;
7215 }
7216 case PPC::LXVP:
7217 case PPC::STXVP: {
7218 // op: XTp
7219 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7220 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 22;
7221 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 17;
7222 // op: DQ_RA
7223 op = getMemRIX16Encoding(MI, 1, Fixups, STI);
7224 op &= UINT64_C(131071);
7225 op <<= 4;
7226 Value |= op;
7227 break;
7228 }
7229 case PPC::PLXVP:
7230 case PPC::PSTXVP: {
7231 // op: XTp
7232 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7233 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 22;
7234 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 17;
7235 // op: D_RA
7236 op = getMemRI34Encoding(MI, 1, Fixups, STI);
7237 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(17179803648)) << 16;
7238 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(532575944704)) >> 18;
7239 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(65535));
7240 break;
7241 }
7242 case PPC::PLXVPpc:
7243 case PPC::PSTXVPpc: {
7244 // op: XTp
7245 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7246 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 22;
7247 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 17;
7248 // op: D_RA
7249 op = getMemRI34PCRelEncoding(MI, 1, Fixups, STI);
7250 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(17179803648)) << 16;
7251 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(532575944704)) >> 18;
7252 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(65535));
7253 break;
7254 }
7255 case PPC::EFDCMPEQ:
7256 case PPC::EFDCMPGT:
7257 case PPC::EFDCMPLT:
7258 case PPC::EFDTSTEQ:
7259 case PPC::EFDTSTGT:
7260 case PPC::EFDTSTLT:
7261 case PPC::EFSCMPEQ:
7262 case PPC::EFSCMPGT:
7263 case PPC::EFSCMPLT:
7264 case PPC::EFSTSTEQ:
7265 case PPC::EFSTSTGT:
7266 case PPC::EFSTSTLT:
7267 case PPC::EVCMPEQ:
7268 case PPC::EVCMPGTS:
7269 case PPC::EVCMPGTU:
7270 case PPC::EVCMPLTS:
7271 case PPC::EVCMPLTU:
7272 case PPC::EVFSCMPEQ:
7273 case PPC::EVFSCMPGT:
7274 case PPC::EVFSCMPLT:
7275 case PPC::EVFSTSTEQ:
7276 case PPC::EVFSTSTGT:
7277 case PPC::EVFSTSTLT: {
7278 // op: crD
7279 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7280 op &= UINT64_C(7);
7281 op <<= 23;
7282 Value |= op;
7283 // op: RA
7284 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
7285 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7286 op <<= 16;
7287 Value |= op;
7288 // op: RB
7289 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
7290 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7291 op <<= 11;
7292 Value |= op;
7293 break;
7294 }
7295 case PPC::EVSEL: {
7296 // op: crD
7297 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(3), Fixups, STI);
7298 op &= UINT64_C(7);
7299 Value |= op;
7300 // op: RA
7301 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
7302 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7303 op <<= 16;
7304 Value |= op;
7305 // op: RB
7306 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
7307 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7308 op <<= 11;
7309 Value |= op;
7310 // op: RT
7311 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
7312 op &= UINT64_C(31);
7313 op <<= 21;
7314 Value |= op;
7315 break;
7316 }
7317 default:
7318 std::string msg;
7319 raw_string_ostream Msg(msg);
7320 Msg << "Not supported instr: " << MI;
7321 report_fatal_error(Msg.str());
7322 }
7323 return Value;
7324}

7330// Bits for subtarget features that participate in instruction matching.
7331enum SubtargetFeatureBits : uint8_t {
7332 Feature_ModernAsBit = 0,
7333};
7334
7335#ifndef NDEBUG
7336static const char *SubtargetFeatureNames[] = {
7337 "Feature_ModernAs",
7338 nullptr
7339};
7340
7341#endif // NDEBUG
7342FeatureBitset PPCMCCodeEmitter::
7343computeAvailableFeatures(const FeatureBitset &FB) const {
7344 FeatureBitset Features;
7345 if ((!FB[PPC::AIXOS] || FB[PPC::FeatureModernAIXAs]))
7346 Features.set(Feature_ModernAsBit);
7347 return Features;
7348}

9832 const FeatureBitset &RequiredFeatures = FeatureBitsets[RequiredFeaturesRefs[Inst.getOpcode()]];
9833 FeatureBitset MissingFeatures =
9834 (AvailableFeatures & RequiredFeatures) ^
9835 RequiredFeatures;
9836 if (MissingFeatures.any()) {
9837 std::ostringstream Msg;
9838 Msg << "Attempting to emit " << MCII.getName(Inst.getOpcode()).str()
9839 << " instruction but the ";
9840 for (unsigned i = 0, e = MissingFeatures.size(); i != e; ++i)
9841 if (MissingFeatures.test(i))
9842 Msg << SubtargetFeatureNames[i] << " ";
9843 Msg << "predicate(s) are not met";
9844 report_fatal_error(Msg.str());
9845 }
